criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — clear mission, scope, inputs and success metrics stated;  
Validate — sensitivity and break-even analysis identified revenue as primary threat;  
Evolve — non-monetary benefits (brand, innovation) explicitly discussed;  
Reflect — final recommendation with concrete contingencies, thresholds, and mitigation strategies.

Discover — stated mission and 10-year horizon guiding the analysis;  
Represent — mapped a year 0–10 cash flow schedule, depreciation and terminal recovery;  
Implement/Validate — used 10-year depreciation/terminal value in code and checked payback vs. project life and sensitivity;  
Evolve/Reflect — discussed long-term strategy risk, abandonment/options and mitigation tied to the 10-year commitment.
